        <abstract> 
<p>Describes a letter he has written to the <hi rend="italic">Athenæum</hi> in which he mentions CL’s views on species modification ["Doctrine of heterogeny", <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 78–80].</p>  
<p>Comments on criticism of Lyell’s book [<hi rend="italic">Antiquity</hi>] by Falconer and others.</p> 
            <p>Mentions his eczema.</p>
            <p>Invites the Lyells to visit.</p>
        </abstract>
